*{{SAMPA|/"ni:grəs/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|es}}

# (''dated or literary; now considered offensive'') A [[black]] female.

====Usage notes====
*In non-black societies its connotation carries an exoticism or mysticism associated with a dark skinned female of African decent.

